parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive engine oil consumption can lead to premature engine wear, engine failure, and potentially cause accidents due to engine seizure or loss of power. It can also result in frequent oil top-offs, increasing maintenance costs and environmental concerns.
symptoms: engine oil level below minimum mark on dipstick
frequent need to add oil between services
excessive oil consumption between oil changes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, putting the driver and passengers at risk of serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag malfunction light comes on and goes off multiple times while driving
the dashboard indicates an "airbag malfunction" after a collision
the warning message "Air Bag System Malfunction" appears on the instrument panel display.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Torque Vectoring and Lane Departure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of torque vectoring or collision avoidance systems can cause the vehicle to jerk to one side, potentially leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly jerks to one side
applying torque to the wrong tires
and the steering wheel moves without human input
attempting to force the vehicle into a different lane.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire failure can cause loss of control, accidents, or vehicle fires, which can result in property damage, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle's tire suddenly becomes flat
causing the vehicle to veer off course

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Blind Spot Warning System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning blind spot warning system can increase the risk of accidents or collisions, as the driver may not be aware of vehicles in the blind spot.
symptoms: The passenger side blind spot warning system functions sporadically
sometimes detecting vehicles and sometimes not
even when driving at the same speed.
